# Dependency Directories
# Node modules folder contains all third-party libraries and should always be ignored.
/node_modules

# Lock File
# Including the package-lock.json is generally recommended for consistency,
# but if you prefer to generate it upon install, you can ignore it.
# However, standard practice often is to INCLUDE package-lock.json.
# Given your explicit mention, we will ignore it if you do not want it.
# If you want consistency across installations (recommended), REMOVE the line below.
/package-lock.json

# Optional: Logs and Temp files
# Logs and temporary files generated during development (good practice to include)
/npm-debug.log
/.DS_Store
/temp